body:
### Welcome to JW Ranch.
This is my first website. I am looking to expand my knowledge in Git repository, HTML, and embedded software engineering. 

### What I do
I am a software engineer in the Aerospace Industry. I have 6 years experience working for Defense Contractors and I am currently working on expanding my skills in embedded software engineering. I have 5 years experience in java standalone application development, testing, and some j2ee. 



### What I did and where I come from
I come from a long family history of military service. Most of my family has served in the Air Force or Army. I grew up knowing the military life and followed my family footsteps and joined the Army for 4 and a half years. I also did 3 years in the National Guard in Tallahassee, FL while attending college at Florida State. I currently have two degrees, an Associates Degree in General Studies from Central Texas College and a Bachelor's in Science Degree in Computer Science from Florida State.
